<para>The <bold>IADLXInterface</bold> is the fundamental interface of ADLX because it is inherited by the majority of the ADLX interfaces. <bold>IADLXInterface</bold> provides methods to control the lifetime of self-destructing ADLX objects, using the reference-counting technique.</para>
